  "title": "通话声音很小或有杂音，如何解决？",
  "answer": " <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  请在信号较好的环境下通话。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  手持模式下通话时，请适当调整握姿。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">将耳朵对准听筒的位置，可有效提高通话音量。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:2.0cm;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">请注意不要用手指或其他物体遮挡住麦克风（通常在手机底部）。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  手持模式下通话时，请注意声源距离麦克风10cm以内。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  耳机模式下通话时声音很小或有杂音，请使用华为标配耳机进行通话，非标配耳机可能会出现不兼容的情况。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  通话过程中按音量上键可以提高通话音量。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  请尽量在噪音干扰小的环境中进行通话。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:4.0pt;margin-left:56.75pt;text-indent:-14.2pt;line-height:12.0pt;tab-stops:list 42.55pt;layout-grid-mode:char;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">l  若问题依然存在，请重启手机或备份重要数据后恢复出厂设置。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">若重启手机或恢复出厂设置后通话仍然有问题，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</p> <p style=\"margin-top:8.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:42.55pt;line-height:12.0pt;layout-grid-mode:char;punctuation-trim:leading;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif'\">华为会定期在官网发布最新软件版本，以优化软件性能，请您及时升级软件，以体验更好的手机性能。</p>",
